description: BRAPPER is an Ethereum based token designed to help facilitate overall adoption of cryptocurrency into currently used platforms. Giving users the power of cryptocurrency by having them include their Ethereum wallet addresses in their current social media profiles. From Facebook to YouTube, Instagram, Twitter, and Twitch, BRAPPER will make it easy for everyone to realize the true power they can have over their own privacy and financial future. BRAPPER is the BRIDGE to mainstream adoption.
name: BrapperToken
